e: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"></b><br></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">B.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al proprietăţii mijloacelor de producţie în sectorul micii producţii de mărfuri din agricultură,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.I/1957, p.103</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii generale asupra dreptului de proprietate cooperatist-colectivistă şi apărarea lui prin revendicare,&nbsp;</em>în „Probleme privind dezvoltarea şi apărarea proprietăţii socialiste în dreptul Republicii Populare Române”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1959, p.95</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Planul cooperatist al lui Lenin şi aspectele juridice ale transformării socialiste a agriculturii în R.P.R.,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1960, p.41</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator</strong> <strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte juridice privind activitatea S.M.T., valorificarea de către gospodăriile colective, pe cale de contractări, a produselor agricole şi dezvoltarea legăturilor intercolective,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1962, p.278</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Legătura dintre contractele încheiate de gospodăriile colective şi planul de producţie,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1963, p.629</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Clasificarea obiectelor proprietăţii colectiviste şi regimul juridic al terenurilor şi diverselor gripe de bunuri şi fonduri băneşti alcătuind patrimoniul unei gospodării agricole colective,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1963, p.185</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brãdeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La défense du droit de propriété coopérative-collectiviste par la voie de la revendication,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1964, p.159</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Lucian Stângu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Natura juridică a normelor de recomandare,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1965, p.81</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al apelor în sistemul proprietăţii socialiste,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1965, p.405</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Petre Marica,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare în dreptul cooperatist-agricol,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1965, p.505</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Petre Marica,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Noul Statut al cooperativei agricole de producţie. Câteva precizări de ordin juridic,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.317</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brãdeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L’approfondissement et l’élargissement de la démocratie coopérative à la lumière du nouveau Statut de la coopérative agricole de production,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1967, p.67</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Salvator Brădeanu, Petre Marica, Lucian Stângu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Tratat de drept cooperatist agricol, vol. I, Partea generală. Raporturile juridice interne,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1968, 348 p.<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salavtor Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mărirea suprafeţelor agricole şi raţionala folosire a terenurilor alcătuind fondul funciar – cerinţă obiectivă a etapei de desăvârşire a construcţiei socialiste,&nbsp;</em>în „Instituţii şi reglementări în dreptul socialist român”, Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, p.119</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Petre Marica, Lucian Stângu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Tratat de drept cooperatist-agricol,&nbsp;</em>vol. II, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dreptul de proprietate cooperatist agricolă. Raporturile juridice externe,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, 426 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Lucian Stângu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Propuneri privind îmbunătăţirea reglementării unor aspecte ale organizării şi funcţionării cooperativelor agricole,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1969, p.261</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brãdeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspects juridques de la coopération artisanal à la lumière de la nouvelle réglementation,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1969, p.227</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brãdeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les aspects juridiques des mesures prises puor l’utilisation adéquate des terrains agricoles en Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1970, p.85</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte privind reglementarea raporturilor contractuale ale cooperaţiei de consum</em>, SCJ, nr.2/1973, p.207</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Lucian Stângu, Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al cooperaţiei de consum,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1974, 214 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brădeanu, Lucian Stângu, Petre Marica, Marilena Uliescu, Aspazia Cojocaru,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Raporturile juridice ale organizaţiilor cooperatiste în etapa actuală,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1977, 158 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Salvator Brãdeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La protection du fonds agraire dans le droit roumain,</em>RRSJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.1/1978, p.157</p><p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">C.</strong></b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Christian,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unirea gospodăriilor colective mici în gospodării mai mari,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1962, p.244</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif I. Christian,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Raporturi juridice complexe care contribuie la întărirea economică-</em></p><p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">organizatorică a gospodăriilor agricole colective,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1964, p.589<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">- &nbsp; &nbsp;</b></p><p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspazia Cojocaru,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al loturilor date în folosinţă membrilor cooperativei &nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p><p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16p