ocaru, Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte juridice privind dreptul de proprietate în actuala reglementare,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2003, p.265</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspazia Cojocaru, Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre natura juridică a dreptului de preemţiune la vânzarea-cumpărarea terenurilor agricole din extravilan,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2004</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ioan Condor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Stingerea dreptului la acţiune. Vărsarea la buget a debitelor prescrise,&nbsp;</em>nr.1/1978, p.73</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ioan Condor, Silvia Cristea,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Jurisdictional activity of the Court of Audit,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1995, p.191</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-