itatea de exerciţiu a drepturilor civile şi ocrotirea sub aspect patrimonial a lipsei şi a restrângerii acestei capacităţi, în lumina recentei legislaţii a R.P.R.,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.I/1956, p.59</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii generale asupra dreptului de proprietate socialistă de stat şi regimul juridic preferenţial al apărării sale prin revendicare,&nbsp;</em>în „Probleme juridice privind dezvoltarea şi apărarea proprietăţii socialiste în dreptul Republicii Populare Române, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1959, p.39</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Egalitatea sexelor în Republica Populară Română sub diversele aspecte ale vieţii sociale – Realizare iniţiată şi săvârşită sub conducerea Partidului Muncitoresc Român,&nbsp;</em>în „Studii juridice”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1960, p.117</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Ion Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Procedee folosite în ţările socialiste pentru prevenirea conflictelor de legi şi limitele autonomiei de voinţă a părţilor,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1962, p.641</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Persoana fizică în dreptul R.P.R., (</em>sub redacţia prof.dr. Traian Ionaşcu, de un colectiv compus din Iosif Christian, Mihail Eliescu; Petre Anca, Virgil Economu, Yolanda Eminescu, Maria I. Eremia, Valentin Georgescu), Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1963, 445 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu, Iosif Christian, Mihail Eliescu, Virgil Economu, Yolanda Eminescu,Maria Ioana Eremia, Valentin Georgescu, Ion Rucăreanu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Căsătoria în dreptul Republicii Socialiste România,&nbsp;</i>Bucureşti, Edit. Academiei RPR, 1964, 510 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionasco,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La transmission du droit de propriété, la constitution et la transmission des autres droits réels de type nouveau, en droit roumaine,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1964, p.3</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionasco,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La notion de patrimoine et ses fonctions dans le droit civil de la République Socialiste de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1966, p.3</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, &nbsp;Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Concepţia dreptului civil al Republicii Socialiste România asupra nulităţii actului juridic,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.223</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Opera de drept civil a lui Nicolae Titulescu,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.209</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Concepţia dreptului civil al Republicii Socialiste România asupra nulităţii actului juridic,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.223</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu, Mihail Eliescu, Yolanda Eminescu, Virgil Economu, Maria Ioana Eremia, Valentin Georgescu, Petre Anca,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Organizaţiile socialiste ca persoane juridice în România</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1967, 398 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu, Virgil Economu, Salvator Brădeanu, Eugen Barasch, Aurelian Ionaşcu, Mihail Eliescu, Yolanda Eminescu, Ioana Maria Eremia, Eleonora Roman, Ion Rucăreanu, Victor Dan Zlătescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Tratat de drept civil, vol. I, Partea generală</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1967, 490 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Concepţia dreptului civil al Republicii Socialiste România asupra nulităţii actului juridic,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1967, p.19</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Răspunderea civilă delictuală – Culpa ca element necesar al răspunderii -,</em>SCJ, nr.1/1970, p.23</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Fapta ilicită şi elementele răspunderii civile delictuale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1972, p.19</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Răspunderea pentru „fapta lucrului” – art.1000 alin.1 C.civ. Studii privind răspunderea civilă delictuală,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.4/1972, p.579</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Salvator Brădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Drepturile reale principale în Republica Socialistă România,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1978, 246 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Ionescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aplicarea prevederilor legii fondului funciar în practica judiciară,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1995, p.95</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">J.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele reflecţii privind problema elaborării unui regulament de coproprietate,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1986, p.336</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Accesiunea imobiliară artificială,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1990, p.53</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L’accession, mode d’aquisition des droits réels dans le droit civil roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1990, p.147</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele aspecte privind accesiunea imobiliară artificială,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/1990, p.281</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cristian Jora, Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre simulaţia cu privire la preţ. Aspecte controversate,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/1991, p.33</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp; &nbsp; Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dreptul de proprietate al regiei autonome,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.4/1993, p.317</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">L.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Lipovanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Capacitatea civilă, conţinut al legii personale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1969, p.673</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">M.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Teodor Mandrea,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cu privire la aplicarea art.53 alin.2 din Legea nr.10/1968, în cazul în care neîncheierea contractului pentru construirea unei locuinţe este urmarea unor împrejurări independente de voinţa chiriaşului,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1971, p.491</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Lucian Mihai, Alice Kolischer,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Termenul revocării donaţiei pentru ingratitudine,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1985, p.248</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Lucian Mihai,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Obligaţiile locatorului şi natura juridică a drepturilor corelative ale locatarului,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1986, p.10</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Lucian Mihai,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Obligaţiile locatarului în locaţiunea de drept comun,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1987, p.205</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 16px;" data-eapps-font-size="16">Ioana Militaru, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" style="font-size: 16px;">Statutul special al societăţilor din domeniul asigurărilor,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.2/1994, p.161</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 16px;" data-eapps-font-size="16">Mircea St. Minea, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" style="font-size: 16px;">Unele consideraţii relative la înscrisurile constitutive ale societăţilor comerciale,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/1996, p.93</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Ştefan Mirea,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;Reflecţii în legătură cu efectele desfiinţării actului de înstrăinare a unui imobil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.1/1982, p.83</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Irina Moroianu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le régime des biens du patrimoine culturel national,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1976, p.199</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Nicolae Munteanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele probleme în aplicarea legii fondului funciar,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1995, p.91</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Roxana Munteanu, Yolanda Eminescu, Octavian Căpăţână, Ion Rucăreanu, Victor Tănăsescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Societăţile mixte constituite în Republica Socialistă România. Fundamentare – Caractere – Constituire,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1976, 232 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen de practică arbitrală în domeniul dreptului civil. Unele aspecte ale reorganizării persoanelor juridice,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1969, p.283</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La copropriété par appartaments en droit socialiste roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1970, p.75</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les droits de l’acheteur concernant l’utilisation de la chose,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1974, p.231</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Une catégorie nouvelle de droits réele "de type nouveau" – création de la législation socialiste roumaine : les droits de jouissance socialiste sur des biens en propriété individuelle,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1985, p.141</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Noi drepturi reale principale de tip nou reglementate prin Legea fondului funciar,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1986, p.145</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mircea Mureşan, Liviu Pop,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Natura dreptului unităţilor socialiste de a folosi sumele de bani depuse de oamenii muncii ca părţi sociale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1988, p.59</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">N.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 16px;" data-eapps-font-size="16">Simona Năstase, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" style="font-size: 16px;">Unele aspecte teoretice şi practice privind obiectul de activitate al societăţii comerciale,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1994, p.47</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Sache Neculăescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele reflecţii în legătură cu prejudiciile morale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1987, p.331</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor, Traian Ionaşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Procedee folosite în ţările socialiste pentru prevenirea conflictelor de legi şi limitele autonomiei de voinţă a părţilor,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1962, p.641</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">O.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Oprişan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Elemente de morală în conceptul de bună-credinţă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1970, p.49</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Oprişan,</strong> <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Nouvelles réglementations sur la construction de logements propriété personnelle et les rapports de location,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1973, p.269</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Oprişan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Trăsăturile, conţinutul şi implicaţiile noului concept al dreptului de proprietate socialistă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1984, p.42</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Oprişan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul general al proprietăţii în România,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1995, p.5</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">P.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dumitru Paşalega,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cesiunea de creanţă cu titlu de garanţie, mijloc de apărare a proprietăţii socialiste,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1968, p.3</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele consideraţii cu privire la dobândirea terenurilor agricole,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1986, p.40</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Câteva aspecte ale opţiunii succesorale în perspectiva unei viitoare reglementări,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1986, p.341</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii cu privire la calitatea pe care o are destinatarul în cadrul contractului de transport al mărfurilor pe calea ferată,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1987, p.242</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu, Hugo Vitzman,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Opţiunea succesorală în practica judiciară şi notarială,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1989, p.56</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pãtraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Particularités dans la transmission des terrains agricoles dans le droit civil socialiste roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1989, p.117</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu, Cristian Jora,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre simulaţia cu privire la preţ. Aspecte controversate,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/1991, p.33</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Reprezentarea succesorală în perspectiva unei noi reglementări</em>, SDR, nr.1-2/1997, p.79</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu, Aspazia Cojocaru,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Probleme privind regimul juridic al bunurilor aparţinând proprietăţii publice şi proprietăţii private,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2001, p.37</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre condiţiile cerute pentru a moşteni,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2002, p.309</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu, Aspazia Cojocaru,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte juridice privind dreptul de proprietate în actuala reglementare,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2003, p.265</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu, Aspazia Cojocaru,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre natura juridică a dreptului de preemţiune la vânzarea-cumpărarea terenurilor agricole din extravilan,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2004</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Petrescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Contribuţii ale practicii judiciare la aplicarea principiului eticii şi echităţii socialiste în materia dreptului civil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1986, p.309</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; textiei extinctive şi la repunerea în termen în raporturile dintre organizaţiile socialiste,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1964, p.229</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Eleonora Roman, Virgil Economu, Salvator Brădeanu, Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen Barasch, Aurelian Ionaşcu, Mihail Eliescu, Yolanda Eminescu, Ioana Maria Eremia, Ion Rucăreanu, Victor Dan Zlătescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Tratat de drept civil, vol. I, Partea generală</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1967, 490 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Ion Rucăreanu, Traian Ionaşcu, Iosif Christian, Mihail Eliescu, Virgil Economu, Yolanda Eminescu, Maria Ioana Eremia, Valentin Georgescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Căsătoria în dreptul Republicii Socialiste România,&nbsp;</i>Bucureşti, Edit. Academiei RPR, 1964, 510 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Rucăreanu, Mihail Eliescu, Octavian Căpăţînă,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Contribuţia ştiinţei juridice româneşti socialiste la cercetarea instituţiilor fundamentale ale dreptului civil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1966, p.441</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Rucãreanu, Mihail Eliesco, Octavian Cãpãţînã,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La conrtibution de la science juridique socialiste roumaine à l’étude des institutions fondamentales du droit civil,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1967, p.197</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Ion Rucăreanu, Virgil Economu, Salvator Brădeanu, Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen Barasch, Aurelian Ionaşcu, Mihail Eliescu, Yolanda Eminescu, Ioana Maria Eremia, Eleonora Roman, Victor Dan Zlătescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Tratat de drept civil, vol. I, Partea generală</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1967, 490 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Rucăreanu, Yolanda Eminescu, Octavian Căpăţână, Roxana Munteanu, Victor Tănăsescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Societăţile mixte constituite în Republica Socialistă România. Fundamentare – Caractere – Constituire,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1976, 232 p.</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">S.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Andreea Paula Seucan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Încetarea contractului de închiriere a spaţiilor locative,&nbsp;</em>SDR,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.1-2/2003, p.179</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Viorel Stănoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Particularităţi ale raportului juridic al asigurării sociale de stat,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1973, p.59</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Valeriu Stoica, Flavius Baias,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Acţiunea în regres a paznicului juridic împotriva paznicului material,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1987, p.48</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Valeriu Stoica,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte privind rezoluţiunea promisiunii de vânzare-cumpărare într-un caz particular,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1987, p.230</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Surdu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Contribuţia practicii judiciare la consacrarea existenţei dreptului de superficie,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.471973, p.673</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">Ş.</strong></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 16px;" data-eapps-font-size="16">Ovidiu Ştefan, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" style="font-size: 16px;">Consideraţii teoretice asupra titlurilor de credit,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1995, p.37</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dinu Ştefãnescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Contribution à l’élaboration d’une nouvelle définition du droit civil subjectifs,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1993, p. 195</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><br></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">T.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Victor Tănăsescu, Yolanda Eminescu, Octavian Căpăţână, Ion Rucăreanu, Roxana Munteanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Societăţile mixte constituite în Republica Socialistă România. Fundamentare – Caractere – Constituire,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1976, 232 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Simona-Maya Teodoroiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Copnsideration à l’égard de la législation roumaine réglementant le domaine des organismes modifiés génétiquement,</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2001, p.339</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Julian Teres,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" da