data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Cãpãţînã,</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;Les caractéristiques de la nouvelle réglementation légale concernant le commerce extérieur et la coopération économique et technico-scientifique de la République Socialiste de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1972, p.81</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Cãpãţînã,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em></strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La régime jurudique de l’activité en Roumanie des représentations commerciales des entreprises et des organisations économiques étrangères,</em> RRSJ, nr.1/1973, p.55</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Căpăţână,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Extinderea competenţei Comisiei de arbitraj de pe lângă Camera de Comerţ a Republicii Socialiste România,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1973, p.423</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Căpăţînă, Adrian Dimitriu, Nicolae Popovici, Ion Dumitrescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţiuni privitoare la întărirea răspunderii organizaţiilor economice din ţările membre ale CAER în domeniul contractelor de livrare a mărfurilor,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1974, p.19</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Cãpãţînã,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La convention arbitrale de commerce extérieur selon le droit roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1975, p.153</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Cãpãţînã,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La loi aplicable à la convention arbitrale de commerce extérieur,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1976, p.47</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Octavian Căpăţînă,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Litigiul arbitral de comerţ exterior,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1978, 178 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-l