lign: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme accordion-trigger" id="ed-1368559327"><h3 data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;"><a class="wv-link-elm active" href="#!next" spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 31.2px;">Drept Comunitar / Dreptul UE</a></h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-container accordion-content animation-initial" id="ed-1368559330" data-animation="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;initial&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;,&quot;keepHeight&quot;:false,&quot;duration&quot;:&quot;0.5s&quot;,&quot;delay&quot;:&quot;0s&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:{&quot;width&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;},&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;group&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;accordion_9b37&quot;,&quot;behavior&quot;:{&quot;show&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;,&quot;hide&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;}}}"><div class="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme" id="ed-1368559333"><h3 spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;">Publicații</h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-text custom-theme" id="ed-1368559336"><p data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;"><br></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">B.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Balint,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aspecte teoretice şi practice cu privire la răspunderea statelor membre pentru încălcarea dreptului comunitar,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/1999, p.329</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Balint,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele delimitări conceptuale în jurisprudenţa Curţii de Justiţie a Comunităţilor Europene privind relaţia drept comunitar – drept naţional,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2000, p.63</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Balint, Octavian Manolache,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Directivele –</em> <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">izvor de drept comunitar,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2002, p.303</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Balint, Octavian Manolache,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Integrarea europeană şi limitările sau restrângerile de suveranitate, în constituţiile statelor membre ale Uniunii Europene ţi în Constituţia revizuită a României,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2004</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mariana Elena Budău,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Lărgirea Uniunii Europene spre Est în viziunea Tratatului de la Nisa,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2001, p.31</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">C.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Otilia Calmuschi,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii privind procesul de armonizare a legislaţiei naţionale cu legislaţia comunitară,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2004</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constanţa Călinoiu, Verginia Vedinaş,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Introducere în teoria funcţiei publice comunitare,</em>SDR,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.3-4/2000, p.313</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Cătălin Ciubotă,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Organizarea, natura şi funcţiile justiţiei comunitare,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2000, p.307</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Paul Cosmovici,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les communautés européennes et léEtat de droit,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1-2/1991, p.3</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Paul Mircea Cosmovici,</b> <strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Roxana Munteanu</strong>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-