20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">N.</strong></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Adrian Năstase</b>, <i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Clauza naţiunii celei mai favorizate – cu specială privire la la practica convenţională a României</i>, în Instituţii de drept comercial internaţional, vol. II, Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1982, p.159</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Câteva precizări în legătură cu dreptul internaţional privat al coexistenţei paşnice,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1964, p.563</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Quelques précisions sur le droit international privé de la coexistence pacifique,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1965, p.65</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion I. Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le principe&nbsp;</em>jura novit curia <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">en cas d’application de la loi étrangère par les tribunaux de la Républiaue Socialiste de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1965, p.293</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Principiul&nbsp;</em>jura novit curia <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">în cazul aplicării legii străine de către instanţele din R.P.R.,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1965, p.239</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Quelques obligations dérivant du droit international contemporain relatives à l’élaboration par les Etats des normes de droit international privé,</em>RRSJ, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1966, p.265</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion Nestor, Octavian Căpăţînă,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Tendinţe şi contribuţii ale practicii judiciare şi arbitrale în cadrul dreptului internaţional privat român,&nbsp;</em>în „instituţii şi reglementări în dreptul socialist român”, Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, p.279</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ion I. Nestor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Legea cu privire la căsătorie în Republica Populară Chineză,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1984, p.259</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">P.</strong></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Bogdan Pătraşcu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Organizarea avocaturii şi a notariatului în R.P. Chineză,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1984, p.261</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">U.</strong></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Din practica instanţelor române cu privire la recunoaşterea hotărârilor judecătoreşti străine,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1985, p.245</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele aspecte ale dreptului la acţiune în&nbsp;</em>exequatur<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;privind sentinţele străine de divorţ,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1987, p.249</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Recunoaşterea unei hotărâri judecătoreşti străine independent de executare,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1989, p.149</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">O problemă de competenţă în dreptul internaţional privat,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/1991, p.37</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Efectele hotărârilor străine. Condiţia reciprocităţii,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3/1995, p.319<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em></p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ernestina Ungureanu, Leucadia Roşculeţ,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii privind executarea hotărârii străine nepatrimoniale,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2000, p.99</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><strong data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48" style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;">Z.</strong></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Octavian Cãpãţînã,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La reconnaissance et l’exécution des décisions&nbsp;</em><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;"></strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">judiciaires civiles et des sentences arbitrales étrangères dans le droit de la République&nbsp;</em><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Socialistes de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1972, p.285</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme accordion-trigger" id="ed-1368559447"><h3 data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;"><a class="wv-link-elm active" href="#!next" spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 31.2px;">Drept internațional public</a></h3></div><div clas