0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le principe de la responsabilité sans faute dans le domaine du préjudice écologique international,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1992, p.49</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le régime juridique des sites contaminés. Le cas de la Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1994, p.15</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La responsabilité civile pour les activités dangereuses (envisageable dans le cadre du Conseil de l’Europe),&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1994, p.137</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les réglementations favorisant la promotion des zones ptotégées,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1997, p.33</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Principiile generale ale dreptului mediului,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/1997, p.5</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Gestionarea riscurilor datorate dezvoltării biotehnologiei,&nbsp;</em>în Studii de drept românesc, nr.3-4/2001</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Marilena Uliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Agriculture, environnement, alimentation. Fonction et responsabilité de l’agriculteur,&nbsp;</em>în Studii de drept românesc, nr.3-4/2004</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><br></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">Z.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Nicolae Zaharia,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La protection de l’environnement dans la législation de la République Socialiste de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1987, p.81.</p></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme accordion-trigger" id="ed-1368559483"><h3 data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;"><a class="wv-link-elm active" href="#!next" spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 31.2px;">Dreptul Muncii</a></h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-container accordion-content animation-initial" id="ed-1368559486" data-animation="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;initial&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;,&quot;keepHeight&quot;:false,&quot;duration&quot;:&quot;0.5s&quot;,&quot;delay&quot;:&quot;0s&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:{&quot;width&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;},&quot;trigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;group&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;accordion_9b37&quot;,&quot;behavior&quot;:{&quot;show&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;,&quot;hide&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;}}}"><div class="inner"><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme" id="ed-1368559489"><h3 spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;">Publicații</h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-text custom-theme" id="ed-1368559492"><p align="center" style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"></b><br></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">A.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Pavel Abraham, Alexandru Ţiclea,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele consideraţii privind contractul colectiv de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1992, p.37</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mihail Albici,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La participation des syndicats à l’activité normative de l’Organisation Internationale du Travail,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1980, p.83</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mihai Albici,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Special Measure for the Protection of Women and Young Persons in the Process of Work,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1981, p.153</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">I. Popescu-Albota, M. Constanţiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Termenele pe care pot fi încheiate contractele de muncă pe durată determinată şi contractele de muncă pentru îndeplinirea unei lucrări determinate,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1958, p.65</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Antoniu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Repunerea în termen în legislaţia muncii – o cerinţă a practicii,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1975, p.161</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Alexandru Athanasiu, Sanda Ghimpu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Actual problems concerning retirement,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1985, p.19</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Alexandru Athanasiu, Andrei Popescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Condiţii procedurale şi de formă ale deciziei de desfacere a contractului de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1984, p.139</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Alexandru Athanasiu, Sanda Ghimpu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les rapports atypiques de travail. Aspects et formes nouvelles,</em>RRSJ, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1986, p.119</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Alexandru Athanasiu, Sanda Ghimpu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les sanctions applicables pour les violations des disposiytions (normes) de la législation du travail,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1989, p.3</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">B.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Beligrădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii referitoare la Legea nr.12/1971 privind încadrarea şi promovarea în muncă a personalului din unităţile socialiste de stat – Explicarea şi interpretarea unor noi reglementări -,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1972, p.293</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Beligrădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii privind necesitatea reglementării repunerii în termen,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1975, p.163</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Beligrădeanu, Gheorghe Brehoi,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Problematica juridică a legii privind recrutarea şi repartizarea forţei de muncă şi a celei privind încadrarea într-o muncă utilă a persoanei apte de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1977, p.247</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Beligrădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Aplicarea principiilor sistemului de retribuire a muncii cu privire la determinarea drepturilor de retribuire cuvenite personalului muncitor, care, temporar, prestează muncă într-o funcţie sau categorie superioară aceleia în care a fost încadrat,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1978, p.277</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Şerban Beligrădeanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Organul de jurisdicţie a muncii competent să soluţioneze litigiile privind obligaţia de restituire a unor drepturi de retribuire,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1984, p.334</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Gheorghe Brehoi,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Soluţionarea cererii de reintegrare în cazul desfacerii contractului de muncă prin respectarea art.64 alin.1 lit.t din Legea nr.5 din 1978,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1989, p.261</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Gheorghe Brehoi, Sanda Ghimpu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Priorităţi în legislaţia muncii,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1/1990, p.5</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">C.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constanţa Călinoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Soluţionarea litigiilor de muncă în cadrul legislaţiei actuale,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.4/1995, p.285</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">M. Constanţiu, I. Popescu-Albota,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Termenele pe care pot fi încheiate contractele de muncă pe durată determinată şi contractele de muncă pentru îndeplinirea unei lucrări determinate,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1958, p.65</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">D.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Raluca Dimitriu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">On notice requested for termination of Labor Contract,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1996, p.195</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Raluca Dimitriu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Desfacerea contractului de muncă pentru necorespundere profesională. Aspecte procedurale,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/1998, p.245</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Raluca Dimitriu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dreptul lucrătorilor la informare şi consultare,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.3-4/2000, p.283</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">F.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dmitru V. Firoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre natura juridică a raportului de muncă prestat în unele condiţii speciale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1983, p.127</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dumitru V. Firoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Imposibilitatea renunţării la drept în cazul unor litigii de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.4/1985, p.342</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Flitan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Noua reglementare a dreptului la pensie al angajaţilor, expresie a grijii partidului faţă de oamenii muncii,&nbsp;</em>în „Studii juridice”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1960, p.247</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Flitan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Probleme de drept muncitoresc în legătură cu reorganizarea prin divizare (totală sau parţială) a organizaţiilor socialiste de stat,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1960, p.117</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Flitan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Legi antisindicale din România burghezo-moşierească; lupta Partidului clasei muncitoare din România împotriva acestor legi şi pentru o reală libertate de asociere în sindicate,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2-3/1961, p.271</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Constantin Flitan,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Temeiul juridic al răspunderii patrimoniale a organizaţiilor socialiste pentru prejudiciile cauzate angajaţilor prin accidente de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.1/1962, p.97</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Incompatibilitatea, recuzarea şi abţinerea în faţa organelor obşteşti de jurisdicţia muncii,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1965, p.253</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">, Cu privire la natura juridică a plângerii adresate comitetului sindicatului împotriva hotărârii comisiei pentru soluţionarea litigiilor de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1967, p.67</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu, Sanda Ghimpu, Şerban Viorel Stănoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare în dreptul muncii,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1967, p.385</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Contractul de şcolarizare încheiat cu elevii şcolilor profesionale de ucenici,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1968, p.283</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu,</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;Capacitatea minorului de 14-16 ani de a încheia contractul de muncă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1969, p.81</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Floresco,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Problème relatifs au contrat de scolarisation conclu avec les élèves des écoles professionnelle,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1969, p.47</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii despre Organizaţia Internaţională a Muncii, cu specială privire la convenţiile acestei organizaţii,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1969, p.375</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Florescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii asupra abaterilor de la regulile de convieţuire socială săvârşite de angajaţi,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1970, p.33</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Maria Floresco, Leonid Miller,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L’emploi temporaire (y compris la forniture temporaire de personnel),&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1970, p.133</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; fo