oz, Siegfreid Kahane, Ion Oancea, Iosif Fodor, Nicoleta Iliescu, Constantin Bulai, Rodica Stănoiu, Victor Roşca,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Explicaţii teoretice ale Codului penal român, vol.III, Partea specială,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1971, 676 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Vintilă Dongoroz şi colaboratorii</strong>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Explicaţii teoretice ale Codului penal,&nbsp;</em>(reeditare), 6 volume, Bucureşti, Editura Academiei, 2003</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">F.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Adrian Fanu-Moca,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Răspunderea penală a persoanei juridice,&nbsp;</em>SDR, nr.1-2/2004</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Cristiana Filişanu, Dana Popescu (II), Vasile Timofte (I),&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Confiscarea unei sume echivalente. Limite,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.1/1987, p.62</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Cristiana Filişanu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Coautoratul în cazul infracţiunilor din culpă,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.1/1989, p.61</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Cristiana Filişanu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Infracţiunile de serviciu sau în legătură cu serviciul. Sugestii de îmbunătăţire a conţinutului unor incriminări,&nbsp;</i>SDR, nr.2/1990, p.172</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Delapidarea – infracţiune deosebit de periculoasă pentru avutul obştesc şi importanţa combaterii acestei infracţiuni</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>SCJ,<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>nr.2/1959, p.383</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">I. Fodor, V. Dongoroz, S. Kahane, I. Oancea, S. Petrovici,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Infracţiuni contra avutului obştesc,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1963, 481 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Infracţiunea continuată ca formă a unităţii infracţionale,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.4/1965, p.649</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">În legătură cu incriminarea folosirii temporare pe nedrept a unui vehicul cu tracţiune mecanică,</i> SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.365<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare. Infracţiuni în domeniul circulaţiei pe drumurile publice,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.2/1967, p.247</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor, Nicoleta Iliescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Suspendarea condiţionată a executării pedepsei în dreptul penal român,</i> SCJ, nr.<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>1/1968, p.59</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Fodor, Vintilă Dongoroz, Siegfreid Kahane, Ion Oancea, Nicoleta Iliescu, Constantin Bulai, Rodica Stănoiu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Explicaţii teoretice ale Codului penal român,&nbsp;</em>vol.I, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Partea generală,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, 436 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Principiile, categoriile şi instituţiile de bază ale noului Cod penal,&nbsp;</em>în „Instituţii şi reglementări în dreptul socialist român”, Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, p.201</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le nouveau Code pénal roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1969, p.3</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Concursul de conexitate (concursul caracterizat) în noul Cod penal,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.2/1969, p. 243</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Fodor, Vintilă Dongoroz, Siegfreid Kahane, Ion Oancea, Nicoleta Iliescu, Constantin Bulai, Rodica Stănoiu, Victor Roşca,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Explicaţii teoretice ale Codului penal român,&nbsp;</em>vol.II, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Partea generală,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1970, 469 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">, Infracţiunea de pericol în dreptul penal român,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.1/1970, p.115</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Iosif Fodor,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Noţiunea de infracţiunea economică</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>SDR, nr.3/1993, p.211</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Iosif Fodor, Vintilă Dongoroz, Siegfreid Kahane, Ion Oancea, Nicoleta Iliescu, Constantin Bulai, Rodica Stănoiu, Victor Roşca,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Explicaţii teoretice ale Codului penal român, vol.III, Partea specială,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1971, 676 p.</p