993, p.63</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Ioan Griga,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Infracţiuni privitoare la societăţile comerciale,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SDR, nr.2/1994, p.153</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">H.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Vladimir Hanga,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Delictele informatice</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.3/1986, p.270</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">I.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Nicoleta Iliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Problema incriminării şi sancţionării actelor preparatorii,&nbsp;</em>în „Studii juridice”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1960, p.481</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Nicoleta Iliescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Infracţiunile ce privesc avutul obştesc în sistemul Codului penal al R.P.R. ,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.4/1960, p.657</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Nicoleta Iliesco,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L’influence sociale dans le domaine de l’illicite pénale,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1964, p.189</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-