ctelor de procedură civilă,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1985, p.62</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">V.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Alexandru Velescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Participarea procurorului la procesul civil în Republica Populară Română,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1958, p.87</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">Z.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Executarea silită în temeiul unor creanţe împotriva organizaţiilor de stat. Câteva soluţii în cadrul legislaţiei actuale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1958, p.197</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Ion Rosetti-Bălănescu, Alexandru Velescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Un mijloc de drept procesual civil pentru apărarea proprietăţii socialiste: Procedura privitoare la măsurile de asigurare şi la executarea silită prevăzută de Decretul nr.417 din 1958,&nbsp;</em>în „Probleme privind dezvoltarea şi apărarea proprietăţii socialiste în dreptul R.P.R.”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1959, p.163</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare în dreptul procesual civil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2-3/1960, p.403</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele probleme ale decontării bancare executorii,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1963, p.461</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">De l’exécution forcée des jugements portant condamnation à une obligation de faire dans les rapports entre organisations socialistes,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1964, p.67</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare în dreptul procesual civil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1964, p.483</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Recursul în supraveghere în lumina principiilor de bază ale dreptului procesual civil al R.P.R. Probleme privind obiectul, termenul de introducere şi procedura în cadrul reglementării actuale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1965, p.225</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le "recours en surveillance" par rapport aux principes de base de la procédure civile de la République Socialiste de Roumanie. Problèmes relatifs à l’object, au délai et à la procédure dans le cadre de la réglementation actuelle,&nbsp;</em>nr.RRSJ, 2/1965, p.263</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Introducere în cercetarea Arbitrajului de Stat şi a practicii arbitrale – sarcinile Arbitrajului de Stat în lumina documentelor Congresului al IX-lea al partidului Comunist Român,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1966, p.243</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Mariana Gheciu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare în dreptul procesual civil. Atribuţiile instanţei de recurs,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1967, p.73</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Executarea silită împotriva organizaţiilor socialiste,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1967, p.411</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;Părţile în acţiunile întemeiate pe dispoziţiile din Legea nr.1/1967, cu privire specială la poziţia procesuală a funcţionarului care poartă răspunderea actului administrativ ilegal,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr. 4/1968, p.573</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Consideraţii cu privire la competenţa comisiilor de judecată de a soluţiona pricini civile,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1969, p.417</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Examen teoretic al practicii judiciare – Subiectele popririi executorii -,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1971, p.319</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La défense de la légalité socialiste et la promotion de la vérité dans l’activité de jugement par la voie du recours extraordinaire en cassation dans le procès civil roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1972, p.41</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Întărirea legalităţii socialiste prin mijlocirea căilor de atac în procesul civil român. Câteva propuneri&nbsp;</em>de lege ferenda<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;în lumina unui nou sistem de judecată,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1979, p.187</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">The role and functions of legal professions,</em>RRSJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.1-2/1982, p.75</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Precizări privind instituţia excepţiilor în dreptul procesual civil,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1983, p.49</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">La participation des tiers aux litiges qui relèvent de la compétence volontaire et obligatoire des organes arbitraux des pays membres du CAEM,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1984, p.35</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Corelaţia dintre recurs şi căile extraordinare de atac,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1985, p.37</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L’éxecution des jugements civils et les moyens de contrainte dont dispose l’instance judiciaire,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1986, p.29</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al nulităţii actelor de procedură în legislaţia procesual civilă (I),&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1986, p.16</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Regimul juridic al nulităţii actelor de procedură în legislaţia procesual civilă (II),&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1986, p.230</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Ion Bãcanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les procédures pour la reconnaissance et l’ex »cution des décisions étrangère en Roumanie,</em>RRSJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1988, p.121</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Viorel Mihai Ciobanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Quelques considérations sur la réglementation procédurale du divorce dans le droit roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1989, p.107</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Savelly Zilberstein, Ion Bãcanu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les voies de recours contre les sentences arbitrales dans le droit roumain,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1998, p.63</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Păstorel Zugrăvescu, Lucian Mihai,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele aspecte privind compunerea instanţei civile în materia răspunderii civile delictuale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.4/1982, p.364.<b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"></b></p></div></div></div><div class="ed-element ed-headline custom-theme accordion-trigger" id="ed-1368559531"><h3 data-eapps-font-size="20.8" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 20.8px; line-height: 31.2px;"><a class="wv-link-elm active" href="#!next" spellcheck="false" data-ms-editor="true" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="31.2" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 31.2px;">Drept Procesual Penal</a></h3></div><div class="ed-element ed-container accordion-content animation-initial" id="ed-1368559534" data-animation="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;initial&quot;:&quot;hide&quot;,&quot;keepHeight&