reptului socialist de inventator – Obiecte, subiecte şi titluri de protecţie,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1970, p.227</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu</strong>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Limitele juridice ale dreptului de citare,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1972, p.391</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu, Sanda Rosetti, I. Iaconachi,</strong> <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Despre necesitatea perfecţionării normelor privind creaţia tehnică,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1973, p.117</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Mărcile de fabrică, de comerţ şi de serviciu,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1974, 241 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu</strong>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dreptul de proprietate industrială, instrument de protecţie a mediului înconjurător,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1975, p.21</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu</strong>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Protecţia juridică a desenelor şi modelelor industriale,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1975, p.215</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Yolanda Eminescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Probleme juridice ale transferului de tehnologie,&nbsp;</em>Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1979, 160 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Yolanda Eminescu</b>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Tratat de proprietate industrială</em>, <em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Vol. I, Creaţii noi,</em> Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1982, 197 p.</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Yolanda Eminescu</b>, 