-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.4/1980, p.321</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dragoş Iliescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Considération sur l’application des méthodes quantitatives au domaine du droit,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1981, p.131</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Dragoş Iliescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Rolul social al dreptului în etapa edificării societăţii socialiste multilateral dezvoltate,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.3/1983, p. 93</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dragoş Iliescu, Sofia Popescu,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Le développement des organes centraux d’Etat de la République Socialiste de Roumanie,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ,<em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</em>nr.2/1985, p.99</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Dragoş Iliescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Unele consideraţii privind metodele şi rezultatele interpretării</i>, SCJ,<i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</i>nr.4/1985, p.294</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Dragoş Iliescu, Sofia Popescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Statul şi dreptul socialist român. Cerinţe actuale în realizarea sarcinilor dezvoltării sociale,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.1/1989, p.5</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Dragoş Iliescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Statul de drept şi libertăţile publice</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">,&nbsp;</b>SDR, nr.3-4/1991, p.123</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Cristian Ionescu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Principiile fundamentale ale dreptului. Concept, esenţă, trăsături definitorii,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.2/1986, p.112</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionasco, Eugène A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Les constantes du droit – Droit et logique -,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1964, p.129</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu şi Eugen Barasch,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Despre</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">relativa independenţă a unor aspecte ale formei în drept. Problema constantelor dreptului,</i><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b>SCJ, nr.2/1964, p.177</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</b><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Dialectica marxistă şi cercetarea juridică. Contribuţii la studiul metodei în cercetarea ştiinţifică pe tărâmul dreptului,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2/1965, p.175</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</b><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Îmbinarea cercetării fundamentale cu cea aplicativă pe tărâmul dreptului,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.3/1966, p.469</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionaşcu, Eugen A. Barasch,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Actele organizaţiilor obşteşti . consideraţii privind explicaţia efectelor pe care le pot produce aceste acte pe planul dreptului,&nbsp;</em>în „Instituţii şi reglementări în dreptul socialist român, Bucureşti, Ed. Academiei, 1969, p.7</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Traian Ionasco,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Quelques considérations sur le droit comparé et les systèmes socio-politiques,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1974, p.47</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">K.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Victor Knapp,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Quelques problèmes méthodologiques dans la science du droit comparé,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.1/1968, p.75</p><p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">&nbsp;</b></p><h2 style="text-align: justify; font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48"><b style="font-size: 32px; line-height: 48px;" data-eapps-font-size="32" data-eapps-line-height="48">L.</b></h2><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ionuţ Lopătan, Cornel Popa, Sorin Stratulat,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Logic, prolog and legal sentence,&nbsp;</em>RRSJ, nr.2/1994, p.175</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ionuţ Lopătan, Cornel Popa, Sorin Stratulat,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Automated Problem Solving and Argumentation,</em> RRSJ, nr.1/1997, p.97</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ladislau Lörincz,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Rolul statului democrat-popular în desăvârşirea sarcinilor revoluţiei burghezo-democratice şi pregătirii condiţiilor trecerii la revoluţia socialistă în România,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.1/1959, p.57</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">L. Lorincz,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Lupta Partidului Muncitoresc Român pentru sfărâmarea aparatului de stat burghezo-moşieresc şi crearea aparatului de stat socialist din ţara noastră,&nbsp;</em>în „Studii juridice”, Ed. Academiei R.P.R., 1960, p.5</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ladislau Lörincz,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Unele probleme ale perfecţionării aparatului de stat în lumina documentelor celui de-al III-lea Congres al P.M.R.,&nbsp;</em>SCJ, nr.2-3/1960, p.295</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Ladislau Lörincz,&nbsp;</strong><em data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">Crearea Partidului Comunist din România – victorie a leninismului în lupta clasei muncitoare pentru cucerirea puterii de stat şi instaurarea dictaturii proletariatului,</em><strong data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;">&nbsp;</strong>SCJ, nr.2-3/1961, p.211</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">L. Lorincz, Anita Naschitz, D. Ciobanu,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Statul şi dreptul socialist sovietic într-o nouă etapă de dezvoltare,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.4/1961, p.495</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">L. Lorincz,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Cu privire la funcţia economică a statului imperialist contemporan,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.4/1966, p.631</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20"><b style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">L. Lorincz,&nbsp;</b><i style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px;" data-eapps-font-size="16" data-eapps-line-height="20">Grupele de presiune în sistemul democraţiei burgheze contemporane,&nbsp;</i>SCJ, nr.4/1968, p.477</p><p style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: ju